channel.title: Dman problem
channel.description:
Wtf is happening. I woke up and my server won't turn on anymore. It's a stable Delta based server. I've had it up and running for around 3 months maybe. I don't see anything wrong with my internet connection or files. I've restarted my computer 3 times along with my router and whole house! Nothing will work. I'm not a noob coder, could anyone help me via team viewer. I just need a second opinion on things. I might shut down my server. There is one person able to login, I have no idea as to why they can only login. I can't even login, only from localhost am I able to login. I said TeamViewer because I don't have any codes to show you. Ask for a code and I'll show you it. Thanks for reading, and hopefully someone can solve my problem.
-Sageofmali

item.title: Dman problem
item.dc:creator: @the_wanderer The Wanderer
item.description:
@the_wanderer wrote:

It is a client problem most likely. It happened to a big server I was part of a while ago. Took them ages to figure it out. Sadly they never told me. I was one of those few who could login. Anyways. Ask what the client is saying when they try to connect. If it says Error Connecting to Server, then I believe I am correct. Although I can’t help you fix it exactly, maybe I limited it down to what you can look at.
